cdata.name: RoyalCoin
cdata.desc: RoyalCoin is a new scrypt based coin created by three Montreal based developers. The block time is set to 3 minutes and the subsidy halves very 600,000 blocks. Difficulty retargets once per day. There was no premine and the orignal block reward was set to 100 RYC with a hard cap limit of 140,000,000.
